dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Scott Phillips. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Scott. My name is Julia Gray.
Nice to meet you, Julia. Could you please provide me with the license plate number of the vehicle involved in the incident?
Yes, the license plate number is Sierra Tango Bravo 8 3 Zulu.
Thank you, Julia. I will also need the date and time of the accident for our records. Can you please share that information with me?
The accident happened on the 15th of May at 3:45 PM.
Thank you for providing that information, Julia. I will now proceed to file a new claim based on the details you've provided.
Thank you, Scott. I appreciate your help in this process.
You're welcome, Julia. If you have any further questions or need updates on your claim, feel free to contact us. Thank you for your time.
